posting_body: ['Location', 'Jamaica .', 'In between 173 and 175 Street Jamaica Ave.', 'Unit is located in 2nd Floor in a brick building.', '( a beautiful apartment.', 'Renovated.)', '1 Bed.', 'Living/Dining.', 'Kitchen.', 'Closets.', '1 Full Bath.', 'Wood floor.', 'Granite counter.', 'Granite eating table.', 'Wood cabinets.', 'SS Refrigerator and SS Stove)', 'F- Subway Train only 5 minutes walking.', '4 Blocks (169 St. Hillside Ave ).', 'J- and E Train Just 8 blocks or five minutes by bus.', 'Banks, Shopping Center, LIR, School, Home Depot, Key Food, Restaurants, Wall Green, Doctors Office, Worships, Groceries, Laundromat, York Collage and University only walking.', 'School : Elementary and Jr. High School Q 168 (Specialized School) next to the building (one block).', 'For viewing the apartment Pl. text me the following :', "Don't call me pl.", 'Just text me the below information for appointment pl.', '(1) Your full name.', '(2) Your current Monthly income either cash or checks or source of income (3) Your credit score (4) Your profession and job description.', '(5) Length of service there ( Total family members (adults and kids).', '347-750-9579 (Shoikat)', 'Rent: $ 1600.00', 'Re/Brokerage Fees: $ 1600.00', 'Security Deposit : $ 1600.00', 'Bills: Tenants pay = Electricity and Gas (Heat runs by gas) ( only two base board heat may be monthly $30 to $40 dollars).', '347-750-9579']
